                           </dimensions>
                        </extent>



                        <foliation>
                           <p>360 folios (+ 4 unfoliated paper flyleaves at the beginning and 2 at
                              the end, and the old leather binding). </p>
                        </foliation>



                        <collation>
                           <p>Quires of mostly 6 to 8 leaves each. </p>
                        </collation>



                        <condition>
                           <p>Damp, with tidemarks across the leaves. </p>
                           <p>Usage stains, mould spotting. </p>
                           <p>Slight worming. </p>
                           <p>Losses at edges, all infilled before rebinding. </p>
                        </condition>



                     </supportDesc>



                     <layoutDesc>



                        <layout columns="1" ruledLines="33 35" writtenLines="33 35">
                           <p>Uniform layout. </p>
                           <p>Larger initial words and titles. </p>
                           <p>Leaf catchwords. </p>
                           <p>Running titles. </p>
                           <p>Marginal notes. </p>
                           <p>Erasures, e.g. folio 75v. </p>
                           <p>A strip of paper inserted between folio 75 and 76. </p>
                        </layout>



                     </layoutDesc>



